<p>
<lb n="1"/>svasti śrīśakavarṣamulu 1170 Agu kīlaka saṁvatsara phālguṇa ba <unclear>8</unclear> sō nāṁḍu svasti śrīmatu nātavāḍi rudradēva 
<lb n="2"/>mahārājula kāketa mailalamahādēvula koḍku mummaḍi <unclear>ga</unclear>ṇaṁpaṭṭavaṁḍu tripurāṁ ttaka dēvaraku Akhaṁḍadīpa 
<lb n="3" break="no"/>mu nētiki Iccina modavulu 25 vīni cēkoni meluṁgu mārebōnikoḍku kōcabōṁḍu tana biḍḍabiḍḍataramu 
<lb n="4"/>nityamāneṁḍu neyi naḍapuvāṁḍu <g ref="sym:doubleBar" type="punctuation">.</g> veṁḍipaṭṭemu 1 <gap reason="lost" quantity="2" unit="character"/> māḍala Ettu Istimi <g ref="sym:doubleBar" type="punctuation">.</g> 
